{"tid":745891,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求救! 貓貓不能從加拿大回港","createTime":"2018-07-17T06:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T10:25:22.000Z","uid":132508,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"746672847ab8aaca350e2d5981fd08fda5df3b23","tid":745891,"uid":132508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:53:41.000Z","msg":"我朋友去加拿大讀書時候收養左隻貓，養左5-6年。<br />\n我朋友已畢業，9月份會返香港，不再留係加拿大，原本計劃同貓貓一齊返香港。<br />\n但點知想申請貓貓回港時有一條大難題，就係香法香港漁護處要保証係屋企10公里以內唔可以有瘋狗症，但我朋友隻貓從來都唔會出街，獸醫亦都証實左佢隻貓貓無瘋狗症，但香港漁護都不受理，因為佢住個到真係有瘋狗症出現過，又無醫生或動物機構可以証明10公里以內無瘋狗症出現。<br />\n<br />\n我又叫我朋友試下報地址報第2度，但因為隻貓貓晶片係落自已地址，所以都呃唔到人，加拿大個邊d動物機構都話幫佢唔到，香港動物入境真係好嚴格。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我朋友喊左好多晚，而家唯有送佢比best friend先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知仲有咩辦法可以幫到佢??"},{"pid":"a0064e9929f71e3d55e7ea00f8ac26a69c8464eb","tid":745891,"uid":49216,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"幫張晶片轉地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話搬左屋無update <br />\n<br />\n利申9up,希望佢地唔洗分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e84442ac4de15978b4c9431b9957b5acfd2b81","tid":745891,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:08:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32e9279daaabe331f9dfc596c7d96b9605461ce2","tid":745891,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"有冇得比多d 錢有公司做偷雞野呀？"},{"pid":"420aea71f77ac8fe5d831fddd97b921a1c89b378","tid":745891,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:14:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fc571a568a2091a52b000b9132f4aeb10913caa","tid":745891,"uid":56999,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"如果其他人又係用呢d招數運動物<br />\n<br />\n令到你隻寵物染到病<br />\n你會有乜野感受"},{"pid":"6bbf8921dc5bef4458d48ebb440a71a226ba451b","tid":745891,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:22:25.000Z","msg":"咁運左番大陸先，再口岸用中港車車落黎囉"},{"pid":"b4db2f2219ec3f2493bab145316ee883e0a657b5","tid":745891,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8738f24947fedd47e20d115604175b2aaf1d953b","tid":745891,"uid":24523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:26:57.000Z","msg":"正路當地漁護（或者相關部門）會出到證明文件話隻貓無事<br />\n可以拎啲相關證明同香港漁護再申請睇入唔入得口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d0ce9c9c0e9ae0d1a03048e5bf602578a5d11a","tid":745891,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:32:07.000Z","msg":"大把方法啦<br />\n<br />\n如果係我果兩隻貓，我天涯海角一切方法都會做"},{"pid":"8ad4f466559d6bd0c5fd55338160b4eaa3a8c590","tid":745891,"uid":112207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b4db2f2219ec3f2493bab145316ee883e0a657b5","tid":745891,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:57:47.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦<br />\n你用正途運隻動物去大陸仲難過運去香港 除非唔洗坐飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9aeb5005b58e308fe59b9875b5c3df1166b57d1","tid":745891,"uid":176063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63bfff591383fe078a04752ee890b34bbbe506fe","tid":745891,"uid":112207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"其實應該要打rabies vac 再驗rabies 抗體level 跟住及格就運得<br />\n點解你好似完全冇人叫你做lee樣野咁既？"},{"pid":"d72049d718e7b15728b503b78473699b2ce94157","tid":745891,"uid":18568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:03:01.000Z","msg":"將隻腦煮熟咪得囉"},{"pid":"d2c1b284ac42d74c01418b70fe1b6f341194c2cb","tid":745891,"uid":18568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將隻貓煮熟咪得囉</blockquote>"},{"pid":"03e6449e7d45b5c0717ff732605b9799ea79a869","tid":745891,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"10公里香港嚟講好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f58ab1a909d53db0350f217e684e2b03557c487","tid":745891,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e6449e7d45b5c0717ff732605b9799ea79a869","tid":745891,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"10公里香港嚟講好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:08:31.000Z","msg":"應該話好大"},{"pid":"05bbfdfe04bf194f7b0be928b6c23c7135aa355c","tid":745891,"uid":112207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63bfff591383fe078a04752ee890b34bbbe506fe","tid":745891,"uid":112207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"其實應該要打rabies vac 再驗rabies 抗體level 跟住及格就運得<br />\n點解你好似完全冇人叫你做lee樣野咁既？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:25:22.000Z","msg":"自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先<br />\n香港去澳洲果d先要打 <br />\n有機會運番香港唔洗打<br />\nBtw<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/182251_5d1f3c1bd99ded649a9e858e81e4dc8e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F182251_5d1f3c1bd99ded649a9e858e81e4dc8e.png&h=3069cfdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我當你果度有瘋狗症係第三組國家<br />\n你填晒佢要既form +要隔離就可以番香港<br />\n詳情： <a href=\"http://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.afcd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fquarantine%2Fqua_ie%2Fqua_ie_ipab%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc%2Fqua_ie_ipab_idc.html&d=ibPqBhc%2FNkKTCLocaVvfiIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=55311cdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/quarantine/qua_ie/qua_ie_ipab/qua_ie_ipab_idc/qua_ie_ipab_idc.html</a><br />\n唔得既你轉過個agent或者去問當地獸醫啦<br />\n希望幫到你"}]}